{"tid":310103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［失物］求好心人 尋失物 卡套","createTime":"2017-07-05T14:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T15:59:01.000Z","uid":12896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52a78cdf52161531d756bae9faca1abf2326613b","tid":310103,"uid":12896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:10:14.000Z","msg":"我幫女朋友尋卡套，請咁多位巴絲幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然唔係咩名牌，但係係我送比佢嘅禮物。<br />\n牌子係Cath Kidston 深藍色，有粉紅色花花<br />\n入面有身分證銀行卡學生證果啲<br />\n<br />\n日期：05-07-2017 <br />\n時間：夜晚大約7-8pm<br />\n地點：銅鑼灣 銅鑼灣廣場/地鐵站 附近<br />\n<br />\n麻煩好心嘅巴絲留意下，我地仲係學生，但會薄酬報告<br />\n見到或者執到就pm me pls"},{"pid":"85736a081934027c7f8b93944c6748c746b0abdc","tid":310103,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:11:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d56968994922d39867a89eedd520bf266ebdfe46","tid":310103,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:11:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84db2f8ef8145bc89e163e621cf7911f2f800d88","tid":310103,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:12:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1514287a3981d8fcf1f8380c05f8f9e1d5bdc4a8","tid":310103,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:12:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5b88e8b1733a98bf27c95c218477e71050fe521","tid":310103,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:13:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試著說「報答」，不要說「報告」。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da34dcf6005eca4f3442472b4bcd9ba47408525b","tid":310103,"uid":12896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:37:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd98f86ab28bce239fbe977f11e561313d30